sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as External Client
    participant Gateway as Istio Gateway/Route<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.3
    participant RestProxy as REST Proxy<br/>8008/TCP HTTP
    participant ModelMesh as ModelMesh<br/>8033/TCP gRPC
    participant Adapter as Runtime Adapter<br/>8085/TCP gRPC
    participant Runtime as Model Server<br/>8001/TCP gRPC
    participant etcd as etcd<br/>2379/TCP HTTP
    participant S3 as S3/MinIO<br/>443/9000 HTTPS/HTTP

    Note over Client,S3: Flow 1: Model Inference Request (REST API)
    Client->>Gateway: POST /v2/models/{model}/infer<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    Gateway->>RestProxy: Forward HTTP request<br/>Plaintext (internal)
    RestProxy->>ModelMesh: Translate to gRPC<br/>KServe V2 Protocol
    ModelMesh->>Adapter: Route to runtime<br/>gRPC
    Adapter->>Runtime: Inference request<br/>gRPC (e.g., MLServer)
    Runtime-->>Adapter: Prediction result
    Adapter-->>ModelMesh: Response
    ModelMesh-->>RestProxy: gRPC response
    RestProxy-->>Gateway: JSON response
    Gateway-->>Client: HTTP 200 OK<br/>Inference result

    Note over Client,S3: Flow 2: Model Inference Request (gRPC Direct)
    Client->>Gateway: gRPC ModelInfer<br/>Auth: Bearer/mTLS
    Gateway->>ModelMesh: Forward gRPC<br/>8033/TCP
    ModelMesh->>Adapter: Route inference
    Adapter->>Runtime: Inference request
    Runtime-->>Adapter: Result
    Adapter-->>ModelMesh: Response
    ModelMesh-->>Gateway: gRPC response
    Gateway-->>Client: Inference result

    Note over Client,S3: Flow 3: Model Loading (First Request)
    Client->>Gateway: POST /v2/models/new-model/infer
    Gateway->>ModelMesh: Request for new model
    ModelMesh->>etcd: Check model metadata<br/>HTTP/2379
    etcd-->>ModelMesh: Model location info
    Note over ModelMesh: Model not loaded<br/>Trigger loading
    ModelMesh->>S3: Download model artifacts<br/>Storage Helper (Init)<br/>HTTPS/443 or HTTP/9000<br/>AWS IAM/Access Keys
    S3-->>ModelMesh: Model files
    ModelMesh->>Runtime: Load model via Adapter<br/>gRPC/8085
    Runtime-->>ModelMesh: Model ready
    ModelMesh->>Adapter: Route inference
    Adapter->>Runtime: Inference request
    Runtime-->>Adapter: Result
    Adapter-->>ModelMesh: Response
    ModelMesh-->>Gateway: Response
    Gateway-->>Client: Inference result

    Note over Client,S3: Flow 4: Controller Reconciliation
    Note over Gateway: User creates Predictor CR
    Gateway->>ModelMesh: kubectl apply -f predictor.yaml
    Note over ModelMesh: Kubernetes API watches CRs
    ModelMesh->>etcd: Store Predictor metadata<br/>Basic Auth
    ModelMesh->>Runtime: Create/Update Deployment<br/>via Kubernetes API<br/>TLS 1.2+ ServiceAccount
    Runtime->>S3: Storage Helper downloads model<br/>during init
    S3-->>Runtime: Model artifacts
    Runtime-->>ModelMesh: Deployment ready
    ModelMesh-->>Gateway: Predictor status updated
